data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after South Wind Community! This exquisite property boasts the largest floor plan in the area with 6 bedrooms, 5 full baths and an unfinished lower level. This beauty has undergone some recent renovations, including a stunning kitchen makeover with top-of-the-line appliances.  The main level greets you with a full bed and bath, perfect for guests. A separate den provides a quiet retreat, while the family room, complete with a cozy fireplace, sets the stage for cherished gatherings. The elegant dining room is ideal for formal entertaining, while the adjacent breakfast area and open kitchen beckon for casual and formal family meals. Step outside to the backyard where an extended deck awaits, offering a serene space for outdoor relaxation and entertainment.  The second level features an oversized master suite with a sprawling sitting area, providing a luxurious retreat for unwinding after a long day. The master bathroom is a sanctuary unto itself, featuring a separate shower and tub combo, as well as his and hers sinks. The master bedroom also boasts an expansive closet, reminiscent of a small office space. Additionally, the second level hosts a versatile loft area, perfect for lounging or quality time with loved ones. Four additional bedrooms and three full bathrooms, ensuring comfort for every member of the household. The laundry is conveniently located on this level well. Bring your imagination to the unfinished basement for additional living space. Don't miss your chance to make this South Wind gem your own!
